600.000 kg bahan pangan?

106
00:09:58,625 --> 00:09:59,426
Belum ditemukan.

107
00:10:01,346 --> 00:10:03,546
Bahan pangan sebanyak 600.000 kg
tidak mungkin menghilang begitu saja.

108
00:10:04,745 --> 00:10:05,346
Nie Chen.

109
00:10:05,625 --> 00:10:06,706
Bawa sekelompok orang lagi

110
00:10:06,706 --> 00:10:08,025
untuk lanjut menyelidiki
keberadaan bahan pangan.

111
00:10:08,306 --> 00:10:09,145
